⚡GUI - UBUNTU

        ◽ sudo apt install -y xfce4 xfce4-goodies
        ◽ sudo apt install -y xrdp firefox filezilla thunderbird  ###These are the packages needed for the project, but you can install any you want
        ◽ sudo adduser xrdp ssl-cert                                    

        ◽ exit  ###Exit root

        ◽ echo xfce4-session > ~/.xsession  ###Create .xsession, to get into the remote connection

        ###Finally, turn on your machine remotely
